A '''foo-twitter''' was a floating device used to distract territorial creatures. Though [[Callista Ming]] and her family originally used one to distract [[wystoh]]s while working in the sea of [[Chad/Legends|Chadra]] on [[Chad/Legends|Chad]], she would later help [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] make one on the ''[[Eye of Palpatine]]'' in order to distract a group of [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorreans]] who were on the ship. The device made noises and sounds to distract whatever type of creature it was supposed to scare off, allowing the creator safety from them.

